Subject: [PATCH] PCI: cpqphp: Fix PCIBIOS_* return value confusion
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e2226dbc4a4919d9c8bd9293299b532090bdf020
